WEBVTT

00:00.326 --> 00:02.454
Finding your way through the airport can be confusing.

00:03.088 --> 00:05.858
Especially when it comes to keeping up with the latest gate changes...

00:06.039 --> 00:07.268
...or where to find your luggage.

00:08.083 --> 00:10.852
But with indoor Google Maps you can easily find your way.

00:11.751 --> 00:15.246
Find your departing gate, your favorite coffee spot,...

00:15.803 --> 00:17.785
...the nearest restroom or a gift shop.

00:18.275 --> 00:19.851
All with just a few taps.

